le power asymmetry or wavelet kurtosis. A trivial\ninterpretation would be that the Bianchi template may require a small\nenhancement of power on scales corresponding to the wavelet scale of 5 degrees.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Feb 2006 18:46:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
