netic field becomes nearly parallel to the disk surface in the high density\nregion. A spiral structure appears due to the rotation and the wound-up\nmagnetic field in the disk.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 2 Feb 2006 06:11:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
